The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, sailing
1. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is not the person traveling to new-york##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | paris  | new-york    |
| Sport   | handball | sailing |

